HEADWORD: Bedsite
<hw>Bed"site`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A recess in a room
for a bed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Of the three bedrooms, two have fireplaces, and all are of fair
size, with windows and <qex>bedsite</qex> well placed.</q>
